<div class="author-card">
    <div class="author-image">
        <img src="/assets/images/cuteimg.webp" alt="Lê Thanh Trúc">
    </div>
    <div class="author-info">
        <h2>Lê Thanh Trúc</h2>
        <p>Tristique volutpat pulvinar vel massa, pellentesque egestas. Est viverra massa quam dignissim aenean malesuada suscipit. Nunc, volutpat pulvinar vel mass.</p>
        <div class="author-social">
            <span><i class="icon-comment"></i> commentaries</span>
            <span><i class="icon-rocket"></i> Rocketbeat</span>
            <span><i class="icon-eye"></i> 72 engagements</span>
        </div>
